creator: chad game
descriptionHtml:
Hide From Daddy: Little Escape is a simple fun game, In this baby escape game you will enjoy the fun of a little "Funny" baby.

🍼 HOW TO PLAY 🍼
- Move the baby with the joystick and avoid the parents to avoid being caught
- Feed the Baby if necessary to get boosters
- Hide behind the tables to get to the objective.

🍼 GAME FEATURE 🍼
- Never get bored with endless level
- Explore multiple playrooms in the house
- Unlock various characters and trail effects
- Animation graphics with cool colors

FIND FUN TIME with our Hide From Daddy: Little Escape !!
descriptionShort: Help little boy escape from getting caught, remember to avoid obstacles
